<li id="cite_note-Eusebius_3.39.3-4-11"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Eusebius_3.39.3-4_11-0">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">Eusebius, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.ccel.org/ccel/schaff/npnf201.iii.viii.xxxix.html"><i>Hist. Eccl.</i> 3.39</a> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20171014085440/http://www.ccel.org/ccel/schaff/npnf201.iii.viii.xxxix.html">Archived</a> 2017-10-14 at the <a href="/wiki/Wayback_Machine" title="Wayback Machine">Wayback Machine</a>.3–4. Translation from <link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1215172403"><cite id="CITEREFBauckham2012" class="citation journal cs1"><a href="/wiki/Richard_Bauckham" title="Richard Bauckham">Bauckham, Richard</a> (2012). <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20141013191250/http://austingrad.edu/images/SBL/Papias%20and%20the%20gospels.pdf">"Papias and the Gospels"</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span>. Archived from <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://austingrad.edu/images/SBL/Papias%20and%20the%20gospels.pdf">the original</a> <span class="cs1-format">(PDF)</span> on 13 October 2014<span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved <span class="nowrap">15 February</span> 2014</span>.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Papias+and+the+Gospels&amp;rft.date=2012&amp;rft.aulast=Bauckham&amp;rft.aufirst=Richard&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Faustingrad.edu%2Fimages%2FSBL%2FPapias%2520and%2520the%2520gospels.pdf&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APapias+of+Hierapolis" class="Z3988"></span> <span class="cs1-visible-error citation-comment"><code class="cs1-code">{{<a href="/wiki/Template:Cite_journal" title="Template:Cite journal">cite journal</a>}}</code>: </span><span class="cs1-visible-error citation-comment">Cite journal requires <code cla